{"tid":639063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄉事派趁機建議放寬僭建","createTime":"2018-04-23T08:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T17:01:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"71964e698eb22eae67224fcc55267e690aba574d","tid":639063,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:18:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180423/20369885?_ga=2.48835494.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F20369885%3F_ga%3D2.48835494.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=PCppDMVJxsBZWbxFIMycxxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=8b2a04a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F20369885%3F_ga%3D2.48835494.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=844804b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180423/20369885?_ga=2.48835494.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄉事派趁機建議放寬僭建<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180423/large/a0802a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180423%2Flarge%2Fa0802a.gif&h=d8322624&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁福元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】現時村屋或丁屋安裝太陽能板高度限制是1.5米，業主不能在天台僭建一層，再於屋頂安裝太陽能板。惟政府公佈上網電價政策後，鄉事派爭取政府放寬僭建政策，十八鄉鄉事委員會主席梁福元不諱言，只要結構安全，政府應放寬太陽能板1.5米的高度限制，容許在僭建物屋頂安裝太陽能板，甚至在棕地、荒廢農地興建太陽能系統。<br />\n<br />\n鄉事派盼政府推動上網電價時，一併將僭建問題解決，惟執法部門表明，仍沿用現有執法標準。屋宇署回覆《蘋果》查詢表明，若丁屋太陽能設施不符合「小型環保及適意設施」規定，即被視為《建築物條例》下的僭建物，署方會按照現行對丁屋僭建物的執法政策，採取執法行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府無意鬆綁<br />\n<br />\n地政總署亦指，如發現村屋有違例建築工程，地政總署會把個案轉介相關部門處理。如違例建築工程同時涉及違反契約條件，地政總署會因應相關部門已採取或將採取的行動，採取適當的執行契約條款行動。<br />\n<br />\n執法部門短期無意鬆綁，主導上網電價的環境局指，與發展局和相關部門密切商討有關問題，研究提供彈性。有環團直言，台灣社會推行上網電價，爭拗8年應否放寬村屋僭建，料香港要解決有關爭議亦困難重重。環境局局長黃錦星早前被問會否放寬1.5米高度限制時，亦未敢承諾，反映政府內部仍未有共識。<br />\n<br />\n■記者潘柏林  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n與承包商分享發電收入　 零成本太陽能　第11年有錢袋<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n招聘條件苛刻　中電承建商被指鋪路聘外勞"},{"pid":"847324110c9370294d6c0f5eff12cc25e50b5b03","tid":639063,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"樓主泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/162100_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F162100_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a3bcb537&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9c5de9e59535267dea490ecdd9d196948a02a5a","tid":639063,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"俾你起夠30層好冇"},{"pid":"7d0239ae2de8fd0d96af4dda9c1fa9bd53414a83","tid":639063,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:22:31.000Z","msg":"最好佢地果邊黎次地震，震到佢地冚家產 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df8ce00cf12ba4d1f346517f04b442be8df3152","tid":639063,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:52:11.000Z","msg":"中國或成為最大的贏家"},{"pid":"29a7121630e3c5f521bfd0a3c1ed39690061fbb9","tid":639063,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0fc7e0f0f05dbf6e2b53da75de7cc5a64d0e3f6","tid":639063,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T17:00:03.000Z","msg":"2047連j屋都無"},{"pid":"19ff62ab70cb941c72fb31d015262a933c420f16","tid":639063,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T17:01:23.000Z","msg":"人心不足蛇吞象"}]}